              support the efforts of World IPv6 Day to accelerate global IPv6 
              deployment. <a href="/press/IPv6 Day-PRrelease">Click here</a> 
              to read the press release.
            </p>

            <p>We were pleased to be a sponsor of <a href="http://www.bsdcan.org/2011/">
              BSDCan 2011</a>, May 13-17, in Ottawa Canada. A big thank you goes out to 
              everyone who stopped by our table and made a donation. We raised over
              $1,000.
            </p>   

            <p>We are pleased to be a sponsor of <a href="http://2011.asiabsdcon.org/">
             AsiaBSDCon 2011</a>, March 17-20, in Tokyo Japan.
            </p>

