      <h2>May-September 2007</h2>
      <p>The FreeBSD Foundation negotiated a joint development agreement with Google, Inc. to
	sponsor FreeBSD developer Joseph Koshy to improve FreeBSD's HWPMC implementation, including
      adding stacktrace support, and a donation of SMP hardware for future SMP scalability work.
	We greatly appreciate Google's support for this project, which will facilitate performance
      measurement and optimization of both the FreeBSD operating system and applications running on
	it. This project has been successfully completed!</p>

